### 17. Analyse AST Python directe
POST {{pythonUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "python",
  "code": "password = 'secret'\ndef foo(a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h): pass\ntry:\n  x = 1\nexcept:\n  pass\nif x == True: pass\nif x == None: pass\n"
}

###

### 18. Analyse AST JavaScript directe (heuristiques)
POST {{pythonUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "javascript",
  "code": "const token = 'Bearer abc123def456';\n// TODO: fix injection\nconst q = 'SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=' + userId;\n"
}

